 * style.answer_padding => 答案区域内边距:number:18|px
 * style.section_padding => 区块上下间距桌面端:number:68|px
 * style.section_padding_mobile => 区块上下间距移动端:number:42|px
 *
 * group:texts => 文本设置
 * texts.title => 区块标题:text:FAQs
 * texts.intro => 区块提示文案:text:Dealer Desk
 * texts.faq_1_question => 问题1:text:Is Indian Rummy Voltage safe for real-money play?
 * texts.faq_1_answer => 答案1:textarea:Indian Rummy Voltage uses protected sessions and transaction checks. Always use the official app source.
 * texts.faq_2_question => 问题2:text:How do I download the latest APK build?
 * texts.faq_2_answer => 答案2:textarea:Use the official download button on this page and allow installation from trusted sources on Android.
 * texts.faq_3_question => 问题3:text:Can I switch between Rummy rooms and side modes quickly?
 * texts.faq_3_answer => 答案3:textarea:Yes. The lobby is designed for quick route switching so you can jump between card modes in a few taps.
